    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/0b69baa1eabd5279a73fd57f80d6d5a0.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/0b69baa1eabd5279a73fd57f80d6d5a0.webm?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Dino Cleanup is a wholesome clean-a-thon platformer with physics-elements and a retro aesthetic.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/d8dbc7a8d704c2323b9a39fc8f6daf77.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/d8dbc7a8d704c2323b9a39fc8f6daf77.webm?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/d8dbc7a8d704c2323b9a39fc8f6daf77.mp4?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/f4c9b21f4d2ddf27ae157658c80647ea.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/f4c9b21f4d2ddf27ae157658c80647ea.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Toxic goop has spread across the dinosaur land! Suck up the mess with your trusty vacuum and save the dinosaurs trapped in the muck. Jump, dash, vacuum, and explore multiple levels full of physics-based fun in a 3D world with 2D pixel sprites! Can you find the source of the goop and restore balance to the dino world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/d7b505bcfab2d3313a74272993a9270d.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/d7b505bcfab2d3313a74272993a9270d.webm?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/53c136d60c1e25d1adb5001824f10b14.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/53c136d60c1e25d1adb5001824f10b14.webm?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/53c136d60c1e25d1adb5001824f10b14.mp4?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/3ebfcd5a4fc2204c6a7eee5406d3388d.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/3ebfcd5a4fc2204c6a7eee5406d3388d.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Explore multiple levels by platforming, interacting with physics objects using your vacuum, and be rewarded for cleaning each level fully </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/acad5a0f2c249206fa88477c7144a828.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/acad5a0f2c249206fa88477c7144a828.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Make dinosaur friends by saving them from the goop, and chat with them back at the hub </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/fc361e4ee38b3ccf1935b35cda5614a2.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/fc361e4ee38b3ccf1935b35cda5614a2.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Find hidden collectibles and exchange them for hats!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/6786299b8b21005e61071071cc08e6ce.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/6786299b8b21005e61071071cc08e6ce.webm?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> Pull and push physics-based objects using your trusty vacuum</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/66dbd715891313924a399c79f8ef71ae.gif?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/66dbd715891313924a399c79f8ef71ae.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span> Unlock new abilities, revealing new ways to play, explore, and clean more efficiently</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/019d3ed918ffc863fa469accf6d54c3b.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/019d3ed918ffc863fa469accf6d54c3b.webm?t=1772139649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/7f16b81e060bdeadc66058df33346381.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/7f16b81e060bdeadc66058df33346381.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=80 height=80 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/8424681437b6148cdf9d689fe65d6bd2.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/8424681437b6148cdf9d689fe65d6bd2.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/c65cbda2fbec582348dd355e0e5eefe9.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/c65cbda2fbec582348dd355e0e5eefe9.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/acad5a0f2c249206fa88477c7144a828.apng?t=1772139649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031750/extras/acad5a0f2c249206fa88477c7144a828.poster.avif?t=1772139649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span></p>",
